snippet.title: Tom Clancy's XDefiant - Worldwide Reveal
snippet.description:
Welcome to the party!

Register now for a chance to playtest early: https://playxdefiant.com    
         
Introducing Tom Clancy’s XDefiant, a free-to-play, fast-paced arena FPS from Ubisoft San Francisco.
Visit https://playxdefiant.com to watch the full reveal and register for a chance to play early!
              #XDefiant

Follow us to catch up on the latest news at: https://playxdefiant.com
https://Twitter.com/PlayXDefiant
https://Instagram.com/PlayXDefiant
https://Facebook.com/PlayXDefiant
